<p>15 April 1915<br/>Thursday</p>
<p>Repeat the dose but go on to the second tower 6 &frac12; miles from camp.<br/>Return very tired   &amp;  footsore.</p>
<p>1915 April 16<br/>Friday</p>
<p>We receive reinforcements in the shape of about 15 officers from the CPRC that is The Ceylon Planters Rifle Corp.<br/>They are very nice fellows but not very good instructors.</p>
